title: OXO 3-Piece Cookie Cutter Set
description: The OXO Good Grips Cookie Cutters make baking cookies fun for all ages. This sweet set includes a 3¼" Biscuit Cutter, Heart Cookie Cutter and a Star Cookie Cutter. All three Cookie Cutters nest neatly for compact storage. The stainless steel blades easily cut through dough for clean, even shapes. Each Cookie Cutter features a wide, flat top for comfortable cookie cutting and is easy for kids to use. Dishwasher safe.

asset.author: OXO

transcripts: Everyone at the OXO office loves when the product teams test products for baking sweets. So I can guarantee these cookies cutters were tested over and over again. The set provides three of the most common shapes for cookies and biscuits . The biscuit cutter, the heart cookie cutter, an the star cookie cutter. The wide comfortable lid on each cookie cutter means that even when you make several dozen cookies, you hands don't get sore. Stainless steel edges easily cut through dough and these cookie cutters are safe for kids to use too. You can pop them in the dishwasher and when you're done, nest them again so they don't clutter your gadget drawer. Here's a good tip, when we sent these to our Japanese office for testing, they decided to use the star shape as a stencil decorating the circle shape with sprinkles.
